{"tid":811670,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"單車手德國女警禾歌，証實半身癱瘓","createTime":"2018-09-09T04:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T11:39:35.000Z","uid":52978,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8290bb26cd31ed8bec3a4c6342573f77cab07d","tid":811670,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n超強實力，場上勁有殺氣，場下又好攪笑<br />\n<br />\n灰，之前以為佢受傷，今日証實癱左<br />\n<br />\n佢仲好積極面對，強！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cc91f6ea884b41021c1fee987baff8fdb3e7ca","tid":811670,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":27,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:40:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a17ef5a9dccd8536729ffaed70878089bbbc523d","tid":811670,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1416841-20180908.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1416841-20180908.htm&d=nLh8YRytU9PsU3PgNBteggCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=4c86c4f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1416841-20180908.htm&h=fe38e40b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1416841-20180908.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n德國著名場地單車手禾歌，6月練習期間脊椎嚴重受傷，她證實腰部以下癱瘓，不能再走路。<br />\n<br />\n多次與禾歌交手的港隊場地單車代表李慧詩形容，是單車界最大的損失，又指一直視禾歌為最強對手，以後無法跟對方比試是終身遺憾。"},{"pid":"ed5578e025007c73aa72e93316d8bfb2c5748099","tid":811670,"uid":205844,"like":2,"dislike":52,"score":-50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"癱咗右未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b893301efb3f337e17275f89dce8ddfa6f61cc4","tid":811670,"uid":52978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"禾歌接受德國雜誌訪問時，形容自己未能再走路十分糟糕，但堅信越快接受現實，越能學習如何面對逆境。<br />\n<br />\n禾歌說，不希望別人只看到受傷的自己，她又渴望成為別人向前的動力泉源。<br />\n<br />\n27歲的禾歌在六月一次訓練時與隊友相撞，脊椎嚴重受傷，送院進行手術。<br />\n<br />\n禾歌在2012年倫敦奧運場地單車賽，帶領德國贏得女子團體爭先賽，四年後的里約奧運，在個人爭先賽八強淘汰香港的李慧詩，再在決賽奪金"},{"pid":"d9e659e7f27f27c50bb6fcf31abc76e615027778","tid":811670,"uid":52978,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"ed5578e025007c73aa72e93316d8bfb2c5748099","tid":811670,"uid":205844,"like":2,"dislike":52,"score":-50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"癱咗右未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"好仆街呢類人，連登界既敗類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995954a9e5a158064ede5167bf51a63a4b331427","tid":811670,"uid":78666,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"d9e659e7f27f27c50bb6fcf31abc76e615027778","tid":811670,"uid":52978,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"ed5578e025007c73aa72e93316d8bfb2c5748099","tid":811670,"uid":205844,"like":2,"dislike":52,"score":-50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"癱咗右未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"好仆街呢類人，連登界既敗類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"直接block"},{"pid":"da82103ed5675adfac4e0e193598e494a364b0fd","tid":811670,"uid":74442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm